data.description: Check out this listing! Two homes, one price.  The main home is just over 1700 square feet with 3-4 bedrooms and large rooms.  The home needs work, finishing touches but the bonus is you can live in the 768 open concept home behind while you work on the main house.  Then use it as a guest house, rental or extended family member. The main house needs painted, some flooring, shower surround installed, ceiling in one bedroom put back up, the central air fixed and whatever else you might like.  Property is strictly sold AS IS.  This property has lots of possibilities, come check it out.
